#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix\\_norm"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.matrix_norm:1 of
msgid "Computes the matrix norm of a matrix (or a stack of matrices) ``x``."
msgstr "计算矩阵（或矩阵堆栈）``x`` 的矩阵范数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.matrix_norm:3 of
msgid "This function is Array API compatible."
msgstr "此函数与 Array API 兼容。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.matrix_norm of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.matrix_norm:5 of
msgid ""
"Input array having shape (..., M, N) and whose two innermost dimensions "
"form ``MxN`` matrices."
msgstr "输入数组，其形状为 (..., M, N)，且最内两维构成 ``MxN`` 矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.matrix_norm:8 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are normed over are left in the "
"result as dimensions with size one. Default: False."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则在结果中保留用于计算范数的轴，并将其大小设为一。默认值"
"：False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.matrix_norm:11 of
msgid ""
"The order of the norm. For details see the table under ``Notes`` in "
"`numpy.linalg.norm`."
msgstr "范数的阶数。详情请参见 `numpy.linalg.norm` 中 ``Notes`` 下的表格。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.matrix_norm:17 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.linalg.norm`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.matrix_norm.matrix_norm:18 of
msgid "Generic norm function"
msgstr "通用范数函数"

